    "seo_text": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div style=\"max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem;\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 16px;\">Buy Wooden Shoe Racks, Cabinets &amp; Wardrobes Online for Modern and Stylish Homes!</h2>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:22px;color:#3a3a3a;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\">Looking to upgrade your space with beautiful and bold furniture? Explore our handpicked yet exclusive collection of <strong>wooden and engineered wood furniture</strong> made for modern homes and busy offices. From <strong>wooden shoe racks</strong> to <strong>compact cabinets</strong> and <strong>spacious wardrobes</strong>, we have everything you need to stay organized in style.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\">Are you a new Snicker head and in need of a stylish shoe organizer? Look no more! Our <strong>wooden shoe racks</strong> offer sleek solutions to keep your footwear in place while adding charm to your hallway or even your bedroom closets.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\">In need of more storage in your living room or bedroom? Choose from our range of <strong>engineered wood cabinets</strong>&mdash;perfect for books, crockery, files, or everyday essentials.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\">Planning a bedroom makeover? Check out our <strong>modern wooden wardrobes for home</strong> that combine style with smart storage. Whether you prefer a classic design or a sleek sliding-door wardrobe, you'll find plenty of options to match your space and taste.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\">Our furniture is crafted from premium <strong>engineered wood</strong>, ensuring quality as well as durability without compromising on style. We offer multiple finishes and sizes &ndash; from bold geometric patterns to aesthetic yet simple pieces to suit all types of interiors&mdash;whether it's a cozy apartment or a spacious villa.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\">Why shop with us? Along with top-notch collection and handpicked design, you get <strong>up to 60% off</strong>, fast delivery across India, and a smooth online shopping experience with our dedicated customer support. Each product is designed to fit right into your home.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0;\">So whether you're furnishing a new home or just adding that perfect cabinet or shoe rack, browse our range today. Your perfect piece is just a click away!</p>\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-4",
        "padding_top": 32,
        "padding_bottom": 32
      }
    },
